OL,4,CTom Kitchin staff suspended amid
OL,5,Cbullying claims
OL,6, Edinburgh chef Tom Kitchin has
OL,7, suspended two members of staff
OL,8, following allegations of "unacceptable
OL,9, behaviour".
OL,11,FIn June, former workers made
OL,12,Fallegations of bullying, violence and
OL,13,Fsexual assault in his restaurants.
OL,15,FOne alleged a chef burned a woman's arm
OL,16,Fwith a hot tray from an oven, while
OL,17,Fanother claimed staff were repeatedly
OL,18,Fpunched if they were not fast enough.
OL,20,FKitchin Group said the claims would be
OL,21,F"fully and independently" investigated.
